<div class="install-page">
  <h1>Install <span style="font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;">tsz</span></h1>

  <div class="install-warning">
    <strong>Pre-release software.</strong>
    <span style="font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;">tsz</span> is under active development and is <em>not</em> yet a drop-in replacement for <code>tsc</code>.
    Diagnostics, inference, and emit may differ from TypeScript today.
    We publish a daily <code>latest</code> PGO-optimized build for the default installer path when one is available for your target.
    Try it for experimentation; do not rely on it for production type-checking.
    Bug reports welcome at
    <a href="https://github.com/mohsen1/tsz/issues">github.com/mohsen1/tsz/issues</a>.
  </div>

  <!-- UNIX_INSTALLATION_BEGIN -->
